Property.Value: This world configuration demonstrates how to make a world that is as flat as possible. In the biome settings height is 0 and biome volatility is set extremely low for smoother terrain. For this example rivers, canyons, caves and vanilla structures have been disabled via the world settings. Resources (ores, trees etc) have been disabled via the ResourceQueue biome setting.
